âœ… Step-by-Step Integration
1. Include ScrollReveal

You already did this âœ…

<script src="https://unpkg.com/scrollreveal"></script>


Keep it above your main.js (which you did correctly).

2. Add the ScrollReveal Script

You can place this inside your /script/main.js or just before </body>.

Hereâ€™s a clean and flexible setup for all your sections ðŸ‘‡

<script>
  // Common animation settings
  const scrollRevealOptions = {
    distance: "60px",
    duration: 1000,
    delay: 200,
    easing: "ease-out",
    reset: true
  };

  // Hero section
  ScrollReveal().reveal(".hero-section .section-content", {
    ...scrollRevealOptions,
    origin: "top"
  });

  // Services section
  ScrollReveal().reveal(".services .content-card", {
    ...scrollRevealOptions,
    origin: "bottom",
    interval: 200 // animates each card one after another
  });

  // Featured products
  ScrollReveal().reveal(".featured-products .product-card", {
    ...scrollRevealOptions,
    origin: "right",
    interval: 150
  });

  // About product section
  ScrollReveal().reveal(".about-product .aboutPro-container", {
    ...scrollRevealOptions,
    origin: "left"
  });

  // Banner section
  ScrollReveal().reveal(".banner-section", {
    ...scrollRevealOptions,
    origin: "bottom"
  });

  // New products (aboutreho)
  ScrollReveal().reveal(".aboutreho .brandimg", {
    ...scrollRevealOptions,
    origin: "bottom",
    interval: 150
  });

  // Newsletter section
  ScrollReveal().reveal(".newsleter", {
    ...scrollRevealOptions,
    origin: "top"
  });

  // Footer
  ScrollReveal().reveal("footer .row", {
    ...scrollRevealOptions,
    origin: "bottom",
    interval: 200
  });
</script>

How It Works

origin â†’ where the animation starts from (top, bottom, left, right).

interval â†’ adds a delay between animations of multiple elements.

reset: true â†’ makes animation reappear when scrolling back.

distance â†’ how far it moves before appearing.

ðŸŒŸ Result

With this script:

The hero section fades in from the top.

The service cards slide up one by one.

The product cards slide from the right.

The about and banner sections fade nicely.

The footer rows appear in sequence.